security enforcement: This new application will be provided with all security check ups which can be performed while, 
encryption and decryption of data.
Its validation and verification process will be done from the server side, which displays the information of various fields, 
such as: new users, existing users, date and time under specified virtual drive. 
The admin of the application will have the authority to set parameters for their various features in the application,
such as lock the account, cancel the transaction, add new recipient, change password etc. 
Its strong bit encryption algorithm will make ensure that others will not able to hack or change their file attributes.

 
